originalText.text: I had an extremely uncomfortable and disheartening experience. Dr. Schaefer's demeanor during our interaction was deeply troubling. He displayed a complete lack of empathy and professionalism, coming across as a narcissist with a god complex, speaking to his patients as if they were beneath him.  I, a Hispanic woman, was made to feel less than, talked down to and had my medical concerns dismissed. No one, regardless of their background, should be subjected to such treatment from a medical professional.

originalText.text:
Ran a bunch of unnecessary lab tests without my permission for just a yearly checkup.  Refused to let me go to the lab myself and insisted on doing it in his office.  This resulted in hundreds of dollars of not insurance covered bills, and I am lucky enough to have very good insurance.  I verified with 2 other doctors the tests were highly unnecessary as I'm a 28 year old with no history of any medical issues at all.
Also just not a very friendly doctor.
